y for our walk-in guests. These walk-in lanes can be reserved using a first come, first serve wait list. Guests must be in the venue to place their names on the wait list. '),(908,109,'dates','2014-02-09'),(909,109,'dates','2014-02-09'),(910,175,'18','Pricing'),(911,175,'19','Weekday Pricing'),(912,175,'20','3PM - 6PM'),(913,175,'21','$35/lane/hour'),(914,175,'22','6PM - 8PM'),(915,175,'23','$45/lane/hour'),(916,175,'24','8PM - Close'),(917,175,'25','$55/lane/hour'),(918,175,'26','Weekend Pricing'),(919,175,'27',''),(920,175,'28','$35/lane/hour'),(921,175,'29','2PM - 8PM'),(922,175,'30','$45/lane/hour'),(923,175,'31','8PM - Close'),(924,175,'40','Groups of 18-45 // 3pm - 7pm'),(925,175,'32','$55/lane/hour'),(926,175,'33','Select your group size'),(927,175,'34','Groups of 1 to 6 people, you can book a single lane online, up to one week in advance. Online reservations will become available through our online system at midnight, 7 days to 24 hours in advance. Once you select a date,  Same day reservations are not permitted as our first come, first serve wait list is in effect upon opening.'),(928,175,'35','Groups of 1-6 Bowlers'),(929,175,'36','Groups of 7-12 Bowlers'),(930,175,'37','Groups of 7-12 people can reserve a two lane bowling reservation two ways: Use our online reservation system for reservations that are less than a week away (only the dates/times available will appear in the drop down menu) OR You can fill out the  and a member of our Events Staff will contact you within 48 hours to set up the reservation.'),(931,175,'38','Groups of 13-18 Bowlers'),(932,175,'39','Groups of 13-18 people will require three lanes, and can be booked up to one month in advance through our Events Department. To submit a request, fill out the Special Events Inquiry Form [link to form] and a member of our Events Staff will contact you within 48 hours to set up the reservation.'),(933,175,'41','Perfect for Happy Hour or Team Building events! Reserving as a Large Party at the Lanes offers priority bowling reservations as well as a pre-arranged Banquet Menu [attach Large Party Menu] to enjoy while at the lanes. A Food & Beverage Minimum will be applied, in addition to bowling charges. Please fill out the Special Events Inquiry Form [link to form] and our Events Director will contact you to set up the reservation.'),(934,175,'42','Groups of 18-45 // Weeknights, 7pm - 12am: Partial Buyout'),(935,175,'43','Whether you\'re celebrating a birthday or a company milestone, the Partial Buyout is a great match! This option provides exclusive use of the Mezzanine for private buffet dining and drinks, followed by bowling on multiple, priority lanes. Based on the event date, a custom Rental Fee will be calculated to include: a Large Party Menu [attach Large Party Menus], alcoholic beverages, and a facility fee. Please fill out the Special Events Inquiry Form [link to form] and our Events Director will contact you to set up the reservation.'),(936,175,'44','Groups of 45-180: Full Buyout'),(937,175,'45','MBC is catered to groups of 45+ people who are interested in reserving our entire venue. Our dedicated Events Staff will work diligently to tailor your experience and create a one-of-a-kind event. Based on the event date and time, a custom Rental Fee will be calculated to include: a Large Party Menu [attached Large Party Menus], alcoholic beverages, unlimited bowling and shoe rentals. We offer in-house AV equipment (projector with a 10 ft. x 12 ft. screen, microphones, and music system). And our bowling staff will provide quality assistance to structure the bowling games to match your groups\' needs. To learn more about a Full Buyout, please fill out the Special Events Inquiry Form [link to form] and our Events Director will contact you to set up the reservation.'),(938,175,'47','Can I make a same day reservation for bowling?'),(939,175,'48','Maybe'),(940,175,'49','Can I make a same day reservation for dining?'),(941,175,'50','Maybe'),(942,175,'51','26'),(943,175,'52','1309'),(944,175,'46','Bowling FAQs'),(945,175,'53','Bowling Details'),(946,175,'54','Please Select a Tab Below'),(950,175,'advertisement','http://development.tier27.com/Mission/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/mbc-2.jpg'),(951,175,'55','http://development.tier27.com/Mission/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/mbc-1.jpg'),(952,175,'56','1312'),(953,175,'57','1259'),(954,175,'58','1512'),(955,175,'59','1311'),(956,175,'60','1310'),(957,175,'61','1501'),(976,175,'faqs','a:7:{s:42:\"Can I make a same-day bowling reservation?\";s:91:\"We do not accept same-day reservations, as our waitlist starts as soon as the venue opens. \";s:65:\"If I reserve a lane in advance, what is your cancellation policy?\";s:327:\"All pre-payments are non-refundable. If you cancel within 48 hours of your reservation date, we can offer a credit with that payment and apply it towards a future booking placed within one calendar year. If you cancel within 48 hours of your reservation, unfortunately the payment is non-refundable and no credit may be issued.\";s:72:\"Why doesn\'t my desired reservation date show up on the booking calendar?\";s:154:\"Only dates with open availability will appear on the booking calendar. Please check our calendar of events for special operating hours and venue closures.\";s:50:\"What happens if I show up late for my reservation?\";s:174:\"As we book each reservation by the hour, we cannot extend the reservation time for any guests arriving late. Your pre-payment reflects only the time in which you pre-reserve.\";s:30:\"Can we eat/drink at the lanes?\";s:163:\"While drinks are allowed directly at the bowling lanes, food may only be enjoyed only at the communal counter space just beside the lanes or within our restaurant.\";s:61:\"Can extra people hang out at the lanes that aren’t bowling?\";s:107:\"Only those who are bowling may be present at the lanes during a reservation, as space is extremely limited.\";s:45:\"Do I have to wear bowling shoes on the lanes?\";s:4:\"Yes.\";}'),(977,175,'groups','a:5:{s:21:\"Groups of 1-6 Bowlers\";s:352:\"Groups of 1 to 6 guests can book a single lane online or over the phone, up to one week in advance. Online reservations will become available through our online system at midnight prior to the preferred date. Only the dates and times that are available will appear. Same day reservations are not permitted, as our wait list is in effect upon opening.  \";s:22:\"Groups of 7-16 Bowlers\";s:351:\"Groups of 7-16 guests can reserve up to two lanes by using our online system (if booking within one week) OR up to one month in advance by contacting our Events Department. For the latter option, please fill out the <a href=\"/event\">Special Events Inquiry Form</a> and a member of our staff will contact you within 24 hours to set up the reservation. \";s:29:\"Groups of 17-35 // Before 6pm\";s:439:\"Perfect for Happy Hour or Team Building events! Reserving as a \'Large Party at the Lanes\' offers priority bowling reservations, exclusive use of our communal snack counter and a custom Banquet Menu to enjoy while at the lanes. A Food & Beverage Minimum will be applied, in addition to bowling charges. Please fill out the <a href=\"/event\">Special Events Inquiry Form</a> and our Events Director will contact you to set up the reservation. \";s:28:\"Groups of 17-45 // 6pm-close\";s:549:\"Whether you’re celebrating a birthday or a company milestone, the \'Partial Buyout\' is a great match! This option provides exclusive use of the Mezzanine for a private dinner buffet and drinks, followed by bowling on priority lanes. Based on the event date and group size, a custom Rental Fee will be calculated to include: a Large Party Menu [attach Large Party Menus], alcoholic beverages and a Facility Fee. Please fill out the <a href=\"/event\">Special Events Inquiry Form</a> and our Events Director will contact you to set up the reservation. \";s:17:\"Full Venue Rental\";s:946:\"MBC can happily accommodate groups up to 180 guests who are interested in reserving our entire venue. From holiday parties to weddings, our dedicated Events Staff will work diligently to tailor your experience and create a one-of-a-kind event.\n\nBased on the event date and time, a Rental Fee will be calculated to include: a customized Large Party Menu, alcoholic beverages, a Facility Fee, unlimited bowling and shoe rentals. Other in-house perks include: projector with a 10 ft x 12 ft projection screen, 2 wireless microphones, customizable music options (including bringing in a DJ), and personal photo display on the bowling screens. Our staff is also fully equipped to assist with bowling tournaments or arrangements to ensure that each guest has ample time to play.\n\nTo learn more about a Full Buyout, please fill out the <a href=\"/event\">Special Events Inquiry Form</a> and our Events Director will contact you to set up the reservation. \";}'),(978,175,'dinner-images','a:4:{i:0;s:4:\"1315\";i:1;s:4:\"2223\";i:2;s:4:\"2213\";i:3;s:4:\"1746\";}'),(979,109,'dates','2014-02-10'),(980,109,'dates','2014-02-10'),(981,175,'100','Come for the bowling, stay for the food! Mission Bowling Club is proud to serve award-winning, elevated comfort food daily beginning at 6pm, as well as an extensive Happy Hour menu beginning  3pm-6pm. '),(982,175,'102',''),(983,175,'105','Groups with 14-17 guests must provide a $75 large party deposit. This payment will be applied towards the final dining bill. MBC will only retain the payment if a cancellation is made within 24 hours of the reservation date. '),(984,175,'104','415.863.2695'),(985,175,'103',''),(986,175,'drinks-images','a:3:{i:0;s:4:\"1499\";i:1;s:4:\"1500\";i:2;s:4:\"1498\";}'),(987,175,'brunch-images','a:3:{i:0;s:4:\"1510\";i:1;s:4:\"1318\";i:2;s:4:\"1511\";}'),(1002,184,'_wp_attached_file','http://development.tier27.com/Mission/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/MBE-1.jpg'),(1003,175,'107','184'),(1004,185,'_wp_attached_file','http://development.tier27.com/Mission/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/MBE-2.jpg'),(1005,175,'108','185'),(1006,186,'_wp_attached_file','http://development.tier27.com/Mission/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/MBE-3.jpg'),(1007,175,'109','185'),(1008,187,'_wp_attached_file','http://development.tier27.com/Mission/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/MBE-4.jpg'),(1009,175,'110','187'),(1010,175,'111','Full and partial buyouts'),(1011,175,'112','Happy hour and birthdays'),(1012,175,'113','Large format dining and prix fixe dinners'),(1013,175,'114','Bowling with drinks and Appetizers'),(1014,175,'116','Looking for an alternative event venue to host your next company outing? Celebrating a birthday? MBC is the perfect destination for an unforgettable event! When mixing bowling, great food and a full bar—there’s no way to lose. Please fill out the information below to contact our Events Director and learn more details. We’re also thrilled to accept inquiries for full-service weddings. Let our staff plan the perfect party!'),(1015,175,'117','Contact Form'),(1016,175,'115','Plan Your Event at MBC'),(1017,175,'118','Mission Bowling Club is a boutique bowling alley that departs from tradition by serving award-winning food and extraordinary specialty cocktails, along with a rotating craft beer and wine list. Our six regulation bowling lanes offer automatic scoring and leather sofas for you to relax in between rolls. MBC is a destination for celebrations of all types, including birthdays, corporate outings, holiday parties, and weddings.'),(1018,175,'119','Owners Molly Bradshaw and Sommer Peterson are proud to bring their eclectic style and experience to add the many other flourishing small businesses in the Mission.'),(1019,175,'120','Our kitchen offers a versatile menu that features locally sourced, seasonal ingredients transformed into elevated comfort food at its best. MBC serves brunch on the weekends, as well as dinner and bar snacks nightly.'),(1020,175,'121','Reservations are highly recommended for both bowling and dining.'),(1021,175,'122','To make a bowling reservation, '),(1022,175,'124','About MBC'),(1023,175,'125','Location'),(1024,175,'126','Contact'),(1025,175,'127','Hours'),(1026,175,'129','Monday – Wednesday: 3pm to 11pm'),(1027,175,'128','MBC is a 21+ venue Monday through Friday'),(1028,175,'131',''),(1029,175,'130','Thursday - Friday: 3pm to Midnight'),(1030,175,'132','Sunday: 11am to 11pm (21+ after 7pm)'),(1031,175,'133','FAQs'),(1032,175,'general-faqs','a:6:{s:32:\"What are your Family Bowl hours?\";s:222:\"We are a 21+ facility every day, except for Family Bowl hosted Saturdays + Sundays between 11am-7pm. The only exception to this rule is for large parties that rent out our entire venue, as guests all ages are then allowed.\";s:30:\"Can we eat/drink at the lanes?\";s:215:\"Guests are able to bring drinks to the lanes, however food must be enjoyed at the communal counter areas just besides the lanes. We recommend dining in our restaurant either before or after your bowling reservation.\";s:58:\"Can extra people hang out at the lanes who aren\'t bowling?\";s:128:\"Space is extremely limited in the bowling area, as MBC has six lanes. Only guests who are bowling may be present at the lanes.  \";s:40:\"What are the hours of the outdoor patio?\";s:58:\"Our covered, dog-friendly patio is open until 10pm daily. \";s:36:\"What is your policy on outside food?\";s:121:\"MBC has a full-service restaurant so guests are only able to bring outside dessert. Please note that there is a $10 fee. \";s:25:\"What is your corkage fee?\";s:15:\"$15 per bottle \";}'),(1037,188,'hours','a:2:{i:0;s:2:\"15\";i:1;s:2:\"16\";}'),(1038,188,'name','Joshua Kornreich'),(1039,188,'company','Tier 27'),(1040,188,'phone','954 882 3115'),(1041,188,'email','joshua.kornreich@gmail.com'),(1042,188,'status','paid'),(1043,188,'notes','Some notes.'),(1044,188,'paid','$140.00'),(1045,188,'datefield','2014-02-10'),(1047,188,'lanes','a:2:{i:0;i:1;i:1;i:2;}'),(1048,188,'bowlers','1'),(1049,188,'price','140'),(1050,181,'reservations','188'),(1053,1